data.text:
Najade delivery schedule in August between 15-21

Dear customers,

We kindly inform you that we because of our Summer and the Hungarian

National Holiday our deliveries are as follows during the month of August:

We are able to process only those orders before 15 August that are placed and

paid by 13 th August at the latest,

Delivery is suspended between 15 -21 August at our webshop and

company.

Please, consider the above-mentioned deadlines when placing your order. We

appreciate your understanding.

NajadeFins Team
